+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| unixODBC                                                    |
| INI lib (libini.so)                                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+

This library provides some usefull functions
for processing INI files (such as odbc.ini).
It is heavily used in unixODBC by the ODBCConfig
and unixODBC Driver Config libs.


